subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Suzann Pettersen shot an even-par 72 to take a one-stroke lead into the final round of the Hana Bank Kolon Championship in Gyeongju, South Korea. Eun-Hee Ji was second after a 68 — the lone sub-70 round of the day.
